3. Score table (Named as `Score`), with fields designed as follows:

| Field   | Type        | Constraints / Defaults                          | Description            |
|---------|-------------|--------------------------------------|--------------------|
| SNo     | varchar(10) | NOT NULL                             | Student ID (FK)    |
| CID     | int         | NOT NULL                             | Course ID (FK)     |
| Score   | float       | NULL                                 | Score              |
| Primary Key   | (SNo, CID) | PRIMARY KEY(SNo, CID)                     | Composite Primary Key   |
| Foreign Key 1 | SNo        | FOREIGN KEY (SNo) REFERENCES Student(SNo) | References Student(SNo) |
